  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I sync my Gmail contacts?",
  "response": "Syncing your Gmail contacts can be done easily through various platforms and devices. Here\u2019s a basic guide on how to sync your Gmail contacts on different devices:\n\n### On Android:\n1. **Open the Settings app**.\n2. **Tap on Accounts or Users & Accounts**.\n3. **Select Google**.\n4. Pick the Gmail account whose contacts you want to sync.\n5. **Make sure Contacts is toggled on**.\n6. After toggling Contacts on, your contacts should start syncing automatically.\n\n### On iOS (iPhone/iPad):\n1. **Open the Settings app**.\n2. **Go to Contacts**.\n3. **Tap on Accounts**.\n4. **Tap on Add Account**.\n5. **Select Google** and sign in with your Gmail credentials.\n6. Ensure that **Contacts is toggled on**.\n   \nAfter setting up the account, your Gmail contacts should start syncing to your device.\n\n### On the Web (Using Google Contacts):\n1. **Open your web browser**.\n2. **Go to Google Contacts** (contacts.google.com).\n3. **Ensure you\u2019re logged into your Google account**.\n4. Your contacts are automatically synced with Google Contacts online.\n\n### On Mac:\n1. **Open System Preferences**.\n2. **Go to Internet Accounts**.\n3. **Click Add another account** and select Google.\n4. Sign in with your Google credentials.\n5. **Ensure that Contacts is checked**.\n\n### Using Microsoft Outlook:\n1. **Download and install the Google Workspace Sync for Microsoft Outlook** via Google's official link.\n2. **Sign in with your Google credentials**.\n3. Follow the setup process to sync your Gmail contacts with Outlook.\n\n### Common troubleshooting tips:\n- Ensure you have a stable internet connection.\n- Double-check that you\u2019re signed into the correct Google account.\n- Restart your device if the contacts are not syncing properly.\n- Ensure any app permissions required for access to contacts are granted.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to keep your Gmail contacts synchronized across various platforms and devices.",
